title: It's Vikings vs. aliens, with Maisie Williams, on this week's Doctor Who - Doctor Who Cult -
text: © BBC Doctor Who pits Vikings against aliens in its next explosive adventure, 'The Girl Who Died'.Game of Thrones star Maisie Williams makes a guest appearance in the episode, but do these new pictures hold any clues as to her character's identity?Williams plays Viking girl Ashildr and the Doctor (Peter Capaldi) seems to recognise her. But from where? Or should that be when? © BBC © BBC Da Vinci's Demons actor David Schofield also features in the new images, sharing scenes with Capaldi's Time Lord.But is Schofield's character Odin really the famous figure from Nordic myth - the same bloke that Anthony Hopkins plays in the Thor movies? © BBC © BBC You'll have to tune into BBC One at 8.20pm this Saturday (October 17) to get all the answers.For an early insight, check out our interview with Capaldi and Jenna Coleman (Clara) from July, where they talked all about "vikings on a spaceship".Doctor Who review: 'Before the Flood' is scary and smartWatch Digital Spy's video review of the latest Doctor Who episode below: function onTemplateLoaded(experienceID) { bcExp = brightcove.getExperience(experienceID); modVP = bcExp.getModule(APIModules.VIDEO_PLAYER); modExp = bcExp.getModule(APIModules.EXPERIENCE); modCon = bcExp.getModule(APIModules.CONTENT); modVP.addEventListener(BCMediaEvent.BEGIN, onVideoStart); modVP.addEventListener(BCMediaEvent.STOP, onVideoStop); modVP.addEventListener(BCMediaEvent.PROGRESS, onVideoProgress); } #_containermyExperience4546229570001 { height: 100%; } // InSkin integration parameters: InSkinParams['myInSkin14546229570001'] = { 'srv_SectionID': '', 'srv_SectionIDPlay': '123757', 'srv_Keywords': '', 'plr_ContentID': 'myExperience4546229570001', 'plr_ContentType': 'BRIGHTCOVE3', 'plr_ContentW': 558, 'plr_ContentH': 314, 'plr_NoSkinContentResize': true, 'plr_NoSkinContentW': 618, 'plr_NoSkinContentH': 348, 'plr_NoSkinInSkinResize': true, 'plr_NoSkinInSkinW': 618, 'plr_NoSkinInSkinH': 348, 'plr_ResizeOnHideSkin': true, 'plr_HideSkinOnExternalAd': 'all', 'plr_ShowSkinAfterExternalAd': true, 'cnt_SmartPlayer': true }; // create the InSkin object: var InSkinObject4546229570001 = new InSkin.Base('myInSkin14546229570001'); brightcove.createExperiences(); if (!navigator.userAgent.match(/Android/i)) { InSkinObject4546229570001.init(); ai_type="video"; }
